<p class="text-sm font-medium leading-normal">Mis Órdenes</p>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg" href="/mecanico/detalle_orden_trabajo">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">build</span>
